A close-up photograph of a server room hard drive array with dozens of status LEDs, all glowing an alarming solid red, casting an ominous crimson glow across gleaming metal server rack surfaces. Cables snake chaotically in the background, slightly out of focus. A single coffee mug sits abandoned on a nearby surface, steam still rising from it, suggesting someone just stepped away in panic. The lighting is dramatic and moody, with the red LED reflections creating abstract patterns on the polished floor. Shot from a low angle to emphasize the imposing scale of the storage infrastructure. Photorealistic style with shallow depth of field.